race.comment: MOET MAGIC (8) finished well back at Q Parklands last time when a 5 length sixth (30.09) but recorded best time of the card when winning four back. Has a solid record over this journey. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Rates on top in this line up. SILVERDALE (1) clocked a new course and distance PB last time, finishing a 4.5 lengths third behind From A Distance in 22.03. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. HARA'S PEST (5) continues to build a strong record and was impressive winner in quick time last start when scoring by a nose (19.75) at Capalaba. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Yet to miss the placings from six starts out of this box. Expected to measure up again. BUSH BOUQUET (3) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.
